## ðŸ—ï¸ Architectural Hard Rules
- **MVVM Architecture**: Strictly follow the View -> ViewModel -> Model hierarchy.
- **File Length**: Any file exceeding 300 lines must be refactored immediately into sub-modules.
- **Feature Isolation**: Create dedicated folders for each feature. Do not "touch" unrelated files.
- **MVP UI**: Always default to premium, high-end aesthetics (Glassmorphism, Lucide icons, no emojis).
- **Audit**: Log all major architectural decisions and changes in `.logs.md`.
